org.archive.wayback.replay.html.rewrite

Class DisableJSIncludeRewriteRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.archive.wayback.replay.html.rewrite.RewriteRule
      • org.archive.wayback.replay.html.rewrite.DisableJSIncludeRewriteRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanNameAware

    public class DisableJSIncludeRewriteRule
extends RewriteRule
    Special RewriteRule for disabling script inclusion (<SCRIPT SRC="..."></SCRIPT>). Policy name shall have script filename, followed by "=". If SRC attribute value contains the filename, SCRIPT tag will be disabled.

    FastArchivalUrlReplayParseEventHandler has special handling of SCRIPT tag. It passes the value of SRC attribute as inputSrc. When this rule returns null or empty string, SCRIPT tag is disabled by replacing SRC attribute value with empty text.

    See Also:
    FastArchivalUrlReplayParseEventHandler, DisableJSBlocksRewriteRule, RewritingStringTransformer
